summary: Return to castle shadowgate in skyrim
descriptionHtml:
A fallen tower in the west of Falkreath holds a portal to a forgotten castle.

 This is an attempt to recreate castle shadowgate in skyrim. This is not complete yet, just a partial walkthrough, most areas are in place. I am uploading the mod to get some feedback, good or bad, on how to finish the mod. Please feel free to comment.
 I am not sure if NMM will work so I disabled it.




DO NOT upload to other sites or use assets without permission,Thanks BG
author: badgremlin
